# Laravel Pint Code Formatter

- If you have modified any PHP files, you must run `vendor/synergitech/laravel-coding-standards/pint --dirty --format agent` before finalizing changes to ensure your code matches the project's expected style.
- Do not run `vendor/synergitech/laravel-coding-standards/pint --test --format agent`, simply run `vendor/synergitech/laravel-coding-standards/pint --format agent` to fix any formatting issues.